    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEMO COMING SOON!<br><br>This top down 2.5D ghost story mystery will take the player through a Louisiana inspired neighborhood haunting. Using foresight, Clair and the player work their way through the looping narrative of one day, to uncover as much of the pieces to the puzzle behind the lingering aparition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141000/extras/8247f88ea5f8d4ffae00709035bb0e0c.avif?t=1771273301\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141000/extras_big/8247f88ea5f8d4ffae00709035bb0e0c.avif?t=1771273301 width=800 height=558 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using Spirit Vision, Clair leaves their body in an astral form to explore the history of the place and dig deeper into the truth of the festering catalyst of its haunting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141000/extras/fbab445da807e4ca4aaaaac7431d51b2.poster.avif?t=1771273301\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141000/extras/fbab445da807e4ca4aaaaac7431d51b2.webm?t=1771273301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141000/extras/fbab445da807e4ca4aaaaac7431d51b2.mp4?t=1771273301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The recently developed neighborhood of Myrtle Grove is filled with an awkward anxiety. The source is the ghost, but is there more affecting the safety or social dynamics of the community? Explore the subdivision as Clair and talk to the curious batch of residents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141000/extras/cb69c0b4d0159f4e13ee311ba1ff21b3.avif?t=1771273301\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141000/extras_big/cb69c0b4d0159f4e13ee311ba1ff21b3.avif?t=1771273301 width=800 height=464 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behind every lingering spirit is an unresolved tragedy. Do you have the courage to find it?</p>",
